{"tid":2364853,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"<OMDB> 丁權批出方式被指違憲 上訴庭裁定政府及鄉黑議局上訴得直","createTime":"2021-01-13T09:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T14:28:37.000Z","uid":101345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e3af96b3885a31db620d99167cc1667eebfc1684","tid":2364853,"uid":101345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T09:54:52.000Z","msg":"「覆核王」郭卓堅及社工呂智恆於2015年入稟高院提司法覆核，指丁屋政策違憲及違《人權法》，要求廢除新界原居民丁權。高等法院早前裁定，部份批出丁權的方式違憲，鄉議局、政府及申請人三方均提上訴。上訴庭今頒下判詞，裁定裁定政府及鄉議局上訴得直，郭卓堅上訴駁回。[url]丁權批出方式被指違憲 上訴庭裁定政府及鄉議局上訴得直<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210113/L7WTN6VXNJCTVMETH5OQZB4I7E/[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210113%2FL7WTN6VXNJCTVMETH5OQZB4I7E%2F%5B%2Furl%5D&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEZKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=25cef26d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210113%2FL7WTN6VXNJCTVMETH5OQZB4I7E%2F%5B%2Furl%5D&h=bcbcd0b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210113/L7WTN6VXNJCTVMETH5OQZB4I7E/[/url]</a>"},{"pid":"7f8420105bea961b1b8f7b06469559bfdea2b6a6","tid":2364853,"uid":101345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T09:57:22.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"244d10186a1f546f9b44d55c125f7d0bb180d5cc","tid":2364853,"uid":242262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:22:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HkiNhJX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHkiNhJX.png&h=8d7371e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"769f3129d0768a7fdde61fdf7980155bf22d571a","tid":2364853,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:28:37.000Z","msg":"牛屎佬係咪大撚曬?"}]}